    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Firmware Update Utility (LFU)</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">The Loadable Firmware Update (LFU) utility runs during power-up -- after the option-firmware scan finds nothing on CD or floppy, the firmware drops to the <text styleclass="Code Example">UPD&gt;</text> prompt. From there you can list and update the firmware images in flash. <text styleclass="Code Example">exit</text> leaves LFU (a reset) and continues to the console.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
